    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the peppers have begun to soften, remove the tray from the oven and switch from the oven setting to medium-high grill</p><p>Add the <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> and <strong>halved green beans</strong> with the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>spiced pepper & green beans</strong></p>",
