    {
      "instruction": "<p>Lay the <strong>tandoori basa</strong> on top of the spiced pepper & green beans and put the tray under the grill for 12-15 min or until cooked through and lightly charred – this is your <strong>tandoori basa, pepper & green bean tray bake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
